name: Unidentified_Aki-Aki_Jedi
content: An Aki-Aki Jedi served the Jedi Order during the High Republic Era. Alongside a Theelin, the Aki-Aki Jedi ventured to the astronomical object Blarrum in the Outer Rim Territories, searching for Triv Blago, a beast-trader who illegally captured and transported dangerous creatures. As the two Jedi searched Kul Kenada Spaceport, the Aki-Aki momentarily sensed Ty Yorrick, a former Jedi Padawan and monster hunter who had been hired by Blago. The two Jedi confronted Blago as the trader spoke with Yorrick, who fled, leaving Blago to the Jedi.
